--- !u!114 &7801499105770383814
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 9072042724292540946}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 6eb329dd0033b984ca71528d4b1c9775, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  recipeNameList:
  - Banh mi
  - Sausage Banh Mi
  - Fried Egg Banh Mi
  - Crispy Roast Pork Banh Mi
  - Sausage & Egg Banh Mi
  - Char Siu Banh Mi
  recipeDescriptionList:
  - Put flour into the Robomixer, let it mix and shape the dough, then place it in
    the oven and wait until it finishes baking to get fresh banh mi
  - Put the sausage on the hob to cook it, then combine banh mi and cooked sausage
    by putting them into the Combiner to get Sausage Banh Mi
  - Put an egg into the Robomixer to crack it, then cook the egg on the hob to make
    a fried egg. After that, combine banh mi and fried egg by putting them into the
    Combiner to get Fried Egg Banh Mi
  - Put the pork into the Cutter to slice it into pieces, then place it in the oven
    to roast until it becomes crispy pork. After that, combine banh mi and cooked
    crispy pork to get Crispy Roast Pork Banh Mi
  - Combine banh mi, fried sausage, and fried egg by putting them into the Combiner
    to get Sausage & Egg Banh Mi
  - Put the pork into the Char Siu Sauce to marinate it, then pass it through the
    Cutter to slice it into pieces. After that, place it in the oven to roast until
    it becomes Char Siu. Finally, combine it with banh mi to get Char Siu Banh Mi
  recipeNameTxt: {fileID: 6098858432786257226}
  recipeDescriptionTxt: {fileID: 3593792979659569553}
